  "body": "\nGrand 4 1/2 à Lasalle<br />\nPropre et bien maintenu<br />\nEspace pour une laveuse et sécheuse<br />\nPlanchers de bois franc<br />\n2e étage d'un 4plex<br />\nProche de la promenade du boulevard Lasalle, rue trés tranquille<br />\nÀ proximité bus 58, 110, 109, 123, 112, 495, 256, 350<br />\nVeuillez contacter Carlo (514) 703-3117 pour prendre un rendez-vous.<br />\n---<br />\nLarge 4 1/2 in LaSalle<br />\nClean and recently renovated<br />\nOutlets for Washer and Dryer (in closed space)<br />\nHardwood floors<br />\n2nd floor of a 4plex<br />\nClose to boulevard LaSalle and place Champlain<br />\nBuses (58,109,123,112,495, 256, 350) in walking distances<br />\nPlease contact Carlo 514.703.3117 for an appointment<!-- START CLTAGS -->\n<br />\n\n\t\t\t<!-- CLTAG xstreet0=7852 Thelma -->\n\t\t\t<!-- CLTAG xstreet1=11th Avenue -->\n\t\t\t<!-- CLTAG city=LaSalle -->\n\t\t\t<!-- CLTAG region=QC -->\n\t\t\t7852 Thelma\n\t\t\t<small>\n\t\t\t\t(<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://maps.google.com/?q=loc%3A+%37%38%35%32+Thelma+LaSalle+QC+CA\">google map</a>)\n\t\t\t\t(<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://maps.yahoo.com/maps_result?addr=%37%38%35%32+Thelma&amp;csz=LaSalle+QC&amp;country=CA\">yahoo map</a>)\n\t\t\t</small>\n\t\t<ul class=\"blurbs\">\n<li><!-- CLTAG catsAreOK=on -->cats are OK - purrr</li>\n<li><!-- CLTAG dogsAreOK=on -->dogs are OK - wooof</li>\n<li> <!-- CLTAG GeographicArea=LaSalle -->Location: LaSalle</li>\n<li>it's NOT ok to contact this poster with services or other commercial interests</li></ul>\n<!-- END CLTAGS -->\n",
